data.name: label14.Text
data.value: Due to the tedious work that Conductors tackle in a day-to-day routine, the chances of them neglecting their duties are elevated. They would likely forget the total earnings in the recent rounds, the passengers that needed to depart in a certain stop, and the most important thing, prioritizing the passenger’s safety.

data.name: label3.Text
data.value: All of us should know that Conductors undergo complicated tasks at once, and as a matter of fact,they spend a fair amount of time multitasking in their field of expertise. By this logic,we created the SeroSete system as the conductor’s reliable friend inside the vehicle.
